  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">You may also opt out of receiving further communications from us or correct your information by sending us a message at unsubscribe@penguinrandomhouse.com. Please note that your request not to receive unsolicited commercial emails from us will not apply to messages that you request or that are not commercial in nature. For example, we may contact you concerning any purchases you have made with us, even if you opt out of receiving unsolicited commercial messages.</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

